{"tid":881895,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國之音(粵語)：習近平巨額資產在香港　有相有地址　如果被人「移動」，點算！","createTime":"2018-10-29T19:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T00:48:04.000Z","uid":47714,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"68903a931c989b0dbda9bb01929fbdbcdc94efe2","tid":881895,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T19:27:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-xi-10102018093050.html?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-xi-10102018093050.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=ea7366ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-xi-10102018093050.html?encoding=traditional</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-xi-10102018093050.html/hk-xi.jpg/@@images/ad03f5e5-7b30-469f-81e9-04c41c1650b5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-xi-10102018093050.html%2Fhk-xi.jpg%2F%40%40images%2Fad03f5e5-7b30-469f-81e9-04c41c1650b5.jpeg&h=460ed257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://vhpd.rfa.org.edgesuite.net/20181010/1251/1_hut7yk22_1_d4l5ku20_1.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvhpd.rfa.org.edgesuite.net%2F20181010%2F1251%2F1_hut7yk22_1_d4l5ku20_1.mp4&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=06f3c60b\" target=\"_blank\">http://vhpd.rfa.org.edgesuite.net/20181010/1251/1_hut7yk22_1_d4l5ku20_1.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/RxKPX9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FRxKPX9&h=5af45849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/1oLgMt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1oLgMt&h=54c24c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/qF3iM8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqF3iM8&h=9d8110de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/DXf2ap\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FDXf2ap&h=dd233aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/Ci2JJT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FCi2JJT&h=598f60f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/qd4aHs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fqd4aHs&h=8bd3995a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ma859c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fma859c&h=4dd3982e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/sKvjVQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsKvjVQ&h=e9cb1be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聲稱致力反腐的國家主席習近平，其家族成員同名同姓登記下，位於香港境內的超級豪宅，周三（10日）在香港被媒體曝光。 令人猜想超級豪宅背後真正擁有人的身份。有時事評論員分析，過去曾有媒體曝光大陸官員或其家族在香港的資產情況，但在近期影星范冰冰逃稅案輿論之下，外界或許會質疑習近平的所謂「反貪」工作。（文宇晴 報道）<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平家族，在香港一直有不動產物業，外界估計市值高達6.4億港元。香港《蘋果日報》周三（10日）曝光，其家族在香港淺水灣獨立屋部份圖則以及內櫳平面圖。報道指，習近平家族成員來香港時，都會在這裡逗留。本台記者曾到過上址查看，該獨立屋重門深鎖，所有玻璃窗都是黑色。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者在香港土地註冊處查得資料（<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-xi-10102018093050.html/hk-xi-doc-1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-xi-10102018093050.html%2Fhk-xi-doc-1.pdf&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=77a69903\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-xi-10102018093050.html/hk-xi-doc-1.pdf</a>），顯示淺水灣獨立屋的業主張燕南，與習近平外甥女的名字不謀而合。她於2009年4月，以個人名義以1.5億港元購入淺水灣麗景道4至10號逍遙居一間獨立屋，現時市值已經逾3億元。此外，記者亦在香港公司注冊處查得，張燕南以一家名為「進意」的公司，持有灣仔會議展覽中心舊翼之上、與甲級寫字樓以及五星級酒店為鄰的單幢服務式住宅「會景閣」38樓一個單位。<br />\n<br />\n記者亦親自前往「會景閣」，賞試證實業主張燕南是否就是習近平外甥女，不過沒有人應門。記者向物業管理人員查詢時，對方稱暫時未見相關單位的住客出入。<br />\n<br />\n物業管理人員說︰這方面不清楚，今天好像沒有見過她。<br />\n<br />\n過去幾年越來越多大陸居民到香港購房，有人是為了炒賣，亦有人是把大陸的資金轉到香港來，方便調動。<br />\n<br />\n香港裝修工程公司負責人黃景釗，過去曾接過不少大陸居民在香港購入豪宅的裝修工程，但期間發生了因為拒絕客人要求挖地牢等違法改建，而被控詐騙。雖然最終官司已被撤訴，不過黃景釗卻至今仍然未收回餘下裝修費。<br />\n<br />\n他向記者反映，他那個官司控告他的客人，一查得知原來是深圳的廳級幹部。<br />\n<br />\n黃景釗說︰我做工程做了幾十年，見盡大上大落的樓價。平時接工程時都不會刻意了解對方的背景，好多（大陸居民）一次過購買4、5個單位，幾千萬一個單位的都有，一次過就過億元了，他們錢在哪裡來了？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/wKuVnt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FwKuVnt&h=f0ca3bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181010/large/a0201c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181010%2Flarge%2Fa0201c.gif&h=822aae0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181010/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181010%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=f98295b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181010/large/a0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181010%2Flarge%2Fa0203a.gif&h=eef981f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/finance/路透-恒大擬抵押灣仔恒大中心-籌117億還債兼派息/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%93%AC%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E7%B1%8C117%E5%84%84%E9%82%84%E5%82%B5%E5%85%BC%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%2F&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=4a35f1ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%93%AC%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E7%B1%8C117%E5%84%84%E9%82%84%E5%82%B5%E5%85%BC%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%2F&h=6a6f4716\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/finance/路透-恒大擬抵押灣仔恒大中心-籌117億還債兼派息/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hui-01_Kntrl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhui-01_Kntrl_1200x0.png&h=22c5a93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n恆大又有資產在港，習總又有資產在港，還有多少中國物體有資產在港？被「移動」怎算？要知香港人很喜歡看人仆街的。"},{"pid":"05ba99366a31c068bf352528eabe26d2f619c749","tid":881895,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T19:32:53.000Z","msg":"打錯標題　係自由亞洲電台先o岩"},{"pid":"509c902b7bd5a1cad48c66b5198236bbeacb1805","tid":881895,"uid":6347,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T19:38:13.000Z","msg":"原來習總都係貪官，好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87aa3cc6408bebb3c08ae72581a8f74a250c8f7","tid":881895,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156637559722357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156637559722357&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=71053f94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156637559722357</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n正如近來的新聞揭露，習近平的資產在香港，恆大有天價資產在香港，他們的痛點，我們接觸得到，並每日在側邊而已。"},{"pid":"7104389abd63095601a8a5d742f2751c39b7f7c4","tid":881895,"uid":70786,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"點解月薪一萬人仔身家可以億億聲嘅呢?<br />\n肯定係成日中六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c91c467ce7b05694924cf1a8c19b4f86b196fb4","tid":881895,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7104389abd63095601a8a5d742f2751c39b7f7c4","tid":881895,"uid":70786,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"點解月薪一萬人仔身家可以億億聲嘅呢?<br />\n肯定係成日中六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" 